\n我由搭lift開始流馬尿 流到返嚟忍住停左<br />\n不過時不時都流幾滴<br />\n依家我仲未平伏到 連透氣聲都覺得嘈<br />\n然而我聽日仲要返工 <br />\n（我抗壓力太低我認）<br />\n<br />\n其實我13號生日 想乞返句 生日快樂<br />\n多謝你睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:39:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好氣餒，下次可以做得更好<br />\n<br />\n同屋企人講番，你都想佢地唔洗咁辛苦"},{"pid":"5e4d1a96576b87e5403a88541c1f071b5dc2d1fb","tid":2380022,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:40:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>舊文黎架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n唔怪得咁熟口臉 <br />\n<a href=\"https://md.hkgolden.com/view_amp.aspx?message=6579452&amp;page=7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmd.hkgolden.com%2Fview_amp.aspx%3Fmessage%3D6579452%26page%3D7&d=KsvwSKeUMZz4C4B35sIM%2BJUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=e1042659\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://md.hkgolden.com/view_amp.aspx?message=6579452&amp;page=7</a>"},{"pid":"de424b53d3d4ac52cb7ced6c8692ae769e30f008","tid":2380022,"uid":62504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:42:07.000Z","msg":"真心 度尺寸都唔識 抵比人鬧wow"},{"pid":"b751d5f0a9221cd2369eab53d68750151b06ee5c","tid":2380022,"uid":77905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:42:50.000Z","msg":"拎去柏傲莊用囉<br />\n<br />\nbtw block <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"722c2eb0030d3fb5f7693453efe4bc27852cb3d5","tid":2380022,"uid":216780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T00:48:58.000Z","msg":"依啲真係有病<br />\n日日作故仔<br />\n真實生咗究竟有幾失敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82b748dda37a44bcc2e6c2d686e9ba99fa81460","tid":2380022,"ui